; Test value date comparison
; Covers value.cc lines 1022-1024, 1027-1029 (date > and date < comparison)

2024/01/15 Test
    Expenses:Food    $50.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/02/20 Test
    Expenses:Food    $30.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format="%(date > [2024/02/01] ? \"after\" : \"before\")\n" Expenses
before
after
end test
